Erlang AMQP Examples

Summary
This is a set of examples that use rebar for building. Source is only slightly
modified to run with newer version of libraries.

Setup
Have rebar in your path.

Compile

  $ cd rabbitmq-erlang-client-examples
  $ make

Network Example
This assumes rabbitmq is already running on your system

  $ cd rabbitmq-erlang-client-examples
  $ make run


Direct Example
Not implemented.

References
1. https://github.com/careo/rabbitmq-erlang-client-examples
